scenarioInformation.title: Error Prevention
scenarioInformation.description:
Congratulations! Atomic Clothing liked your last design so they want you to design another one!

For this exercise, you will be designing Atomic Clothing's account settings page for their e-commerce website. They have requested that the sections are in the following order: Username, Password, Security.

Remember, to make sure the user understands the ramifications of their changes!
